<div id="I_content">
<div class="C_doc">
<div id="I_type">public member function</div>
<div id="I_file">&lt;bitset&gt;</div>
<h1><span class="namespace" title="namespace std">std::</span><a href="/reference/bitset/bitset/">bitset</a>::size</h1>
<div class="C_prototype"><div class="C_SwitchCases">
<div title="C++98">
<pre>size_t size() const;</pre></div>
<div title="C++11" class="on">
<pre>constexpr size_t size() noexcept;</pre></div>
</div>
</div><div id="I_description">Return size</div>
<section id="description">
Returns the number of bits in the <samp><a href="/bitset">bitset</a></samp>.<br>
<br>
This is the template parameter with which the <samp><a href="/bitset">bitset</a></samp> class is instantiated (template parameter <samp>N</samp>).<br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="parameters">
<h3>Parameters</h3>
none<br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="return">
<h3>Return Value</h3>
The number of bits in the <samp><a href="/bitset">bitset</a></samp>.<br>
<br>
<samp><a href="/size_t">size_t</a></samp> is an unsigned integral type.<br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="example">
<h3>Example</h3>
<div class="auto"><table class="snippet"><tr><td class="rownum"><pre><code>1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>11<br>12<br>13<br>14<br></code></pre></td>
<td class="source"><pre><code><cite>// bitset::size</cite>
<dfn>#include &lt;iostream&gt;       </dfn><cite>// std::cout</cite>
<dfn>#include &lt;bitset&gt;         </dfn><cite>// std::bitset</cite>

<var>int</var> main ()
{
  std::bitset&lt;8&gt; foo;
  std::bitset&lt;4&gt; bar;

  std::cout &lt;&lt; <kbd>"foo.size() is "</kbd> &lt;&lt; foo.size() &lt;&lt; <kbd>'\n'</kbd>;
  std::cout &lt;&lt; <kbd>"bar.size() is "</kbd> &lt;&lt; bar.size() &lt;&lt; <kbd>'\n'</kbd>;

  <var>return</var> 0;
}</code></pre></td><td class="C_btnholder"></td></tr></table></div>
<br>
<br>
Output:<br>
<div class="auto"><table class="snippet"><tr><td class="output"><pre><samp>
foo.size() is 8
bar.size() is 4
</samp></pre></td></tr></table></div>
</section>
<br>
<section id="access">
<h3>Data races</h3>
None (compile-time constant).<br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="exceptions">
<h3>Exception safety</h3>
<b>No-throw guarantee:</b> never throws exceptions.<br>
</section>
